&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sweet Tooth&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;During our stroll in the city, we could not resist trying the Polenta e Osei, a special dessert from Bergamo.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

